description: Get durability, function, comfort and style—all in one backpack. The Five Star Angle Zip Backpack includes a laptop sleeve, mesh water bottle pocket, a small item storage pouch and two generously-sized main storage compartments that give you plenty of room for all your stuff. Durable denier polyester with reinforced stitching lasts all year. *ACCO Brands will replace any Five Star Angle Zip Plus Binder that is returned within one year from the date of purchase. The guarantee does not cover damage due to abuse. Contact ACCO Brands Consumer Affairs at www.mead.com for instructions. Accessories not included.
title: Five Star Angle Zip And Backpack, Blue (72382)
